Cyberpunk style: A sprawling neon-lit circuit board cityscape at night, where glowing data streams flow through transparent pipelines connecting towering server monoliths. In the foreground, a series of three massive industrial pipes glow in sequence - the first burning orange, the second electric blue, and the third vibrant green - representing stages of a process. Holographic diagnostic screens float in the air showing abstract geometric patterns and checkmarks. The atmosphere is hazy with digital particles, rain reflecting the countless lights. Chrome and glass structures rise in the background, their surfaces alive with scrolling code patterns rendered as abstract light trails. A lone automated drone hovers near the central pipeline junction, scanning with a beam of cyan light. The color palette emphasizes deep purples, electric blues, hot pinks, and acid greens against a dark metropolitan backdrop.
